  "about": "Age: 13\n\nHinata is the second of the three sisters and a middle school student. She sleeps in late in the mornings until the very last minute and often makes bentos by herself. She calls Rei \"Rei-chan.\" Like her elder sister Akari, she likes taking care of Rei. She has a strong loyalty toward her friends and family and aspires to be as mature as her sister when she gets older.\n\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)",
